###
### =================================================================
### ATTENDANCE API ENDPOINTS (/api/attendance)
### =================================================================
#
# Prerequisite: Run auth.http, courses.http, and lectures.http first.
#

### 1. Mark Attendance for a Lecture (as Student)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance/mark
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

{
  "lectureId": "{{lectureId}}"
}


### 2. Get a Student's Attendance Record for a Course (Self View)
# The student checks their own attendance record for the specified course.
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/student/{{studentId}}/course/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}


### 3. Get the Full Attendance Report for a Course (as Teacher)
# The teacher gets a report of all enrolled students and their attendance status.
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/course/{{courseId}}/report
Authorization: Bearer {{teacherToken}}